Developer Terms of Use
des:
The purpose of the skill is to make people aware of basics of electrical related terms. People donot know these basic terms and electricity plays a vital role in our lives. 

It provides the fundamental definitions of basic terms used in electricity like current,voltage etc.

It works by entering a term which you want to know about by first saying "open electrical geek" then saying like "what is current" or " what is meant by current" etc.. Then it displays the definition of it and then says good bye.
If you want to know more then you should say again "open electrical geek" then you can search again.

The terms which can be searched are: 
current
voltage
resistance
capacitance
inductance
diode
transistor
generator
motor
power
direct current
alternating current


And the ways to ask questions is:
1) What is current
2) what is meant by motor
3) what's current
4) what's meant by transistor

Its a very simple skill to work on and very creative too.
